      {
        className: 'function',
        beginKeywords: 'function',
        end: '$',
        contains: [
          VARIABLE,
          TITLE2,
          hljs.APOS_STRING_MODE,
          hljs.QUOTE_STRING_MODE,

      hljs.C_NUMBER_MODE,
      TITLE1
    ].concat(COMMENT_MODES),
    illegal: ';$|^\\[|^=|&|\\{'
  };
